ngles?chart=4736|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=19 August 2019|accessdate=17 August 2019}}\n* \"Real Thing\": {{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4743|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=9 September 2019|accessdate=7 September 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Golden Years (Ruel and M-Phazes song)|Golden Years]]\"<br />{{small|(with [[M-Phazes]])}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2017\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| {{n/a|Non-album single}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Don't Tell Me (Ruel song)|Don't Tell Me]]\"\n| 86 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n* [[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]]: Gold<ref name=\"ARIA2018\">{{cite web|url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/SinglesAccreds2018.htm|title=ARIA Charts - Accreditations - 2018 Singles |publisher=ARIA|accessdate=21 January 2019}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"5\"| ''Ready''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Dazed & Confused (Ruel song)|Dazed & Confused]]\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2018\n| 53 || 7 || \u2014\n|\n* ARIA: Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA19\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Younger (Ruel song)|Younger]]\"\n| 76 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n* ARIA: Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA19\">{{cite web |url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupagesSinglesAccreds2019.htm |title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations \u2013 2019 Singles |publisher=ARIA |accessdate=22 September 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Not Thinkin' Bout You]]\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(solo or remix featuring [[GoldLink]])</span>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Say\"<br /><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(acoustic version featuring Jake Meadows)</span><ref>{{cite web |url=https://open.spotify.com/album/5OXzSOxo4SmoFMsRURhAFp&ved=2ahUKEwit44bizajoAhWz7XMBHeTHDToQFjABegQIBhAB&usg=AOvVaw1ZlPJjQyyTMu5NZtL1aTCg |title=Say (feat. Jake Meadows) [Acoustic Version] by Ruel on Spotify |website=Spotify |date=14 March 2019 |accessdate=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2019\n| \u201